# Device Diagnostics Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   run_diagnostics — Run remote diagnostics based on device type and symptoms
#   check_software_version — Check if the device is running the latest software
#   get_known_issues — Look up known issues and workarounds
#   reset_device_settings — Generate instructions for resetting device settings
#   check_battery_health — Check battery health and cycle count
